yandex:index/ydbDatabaseIamBinding:ydbDa.description:
## yandex\_ydb\_database\_iam\_binding

Allows creation and management of a single binding within IAM policy for
an existing Managed YDB Database instance.

{{% examples %}}
## Example Usage
{{% example %}}

```typescript
import * as pulumi from "@pulumi/pulumi";
import * as yandex from "@pulumiverse/yandex";

const database1 = new yandex.YdbDatabaseServerless("database1", {folderId: data.yandex_resourcemanager_folder.test_folder.id});
const viewer = new yandex.YdbDatabaseIamBinding("viewer", {
    databaseId: database1.id,
    role: "ydb.viewer",
    members: ["userAccount:foo_user_id"],
});
```
